          "process_md": "&gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Visit the official homepage of the [Sports Authority of Gujarat](https://sportsauthority.gujarat.gov.in/).\n**Step 2:** On the homepage,  navigate to the Player Registration option after clicking on the &amp;quot;Register&amp;quot; button in the top-right corner.\n**Step 3:** Fill out the Player Registration Form with the required personal details and click on &amp;quot;Register&amp;quot;.\n**Step 4:** After completion, the login ID and password information will be shared via email.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n&gt; **Login and Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:**  Go to the [Login page](https://sportsauthority.gujarat.gov.in/login) and select the user type as &amp;quot;Player&amp;quot;.\n**Step 2:** Log in using the credentials received via email.\n**Step 3:** After logging in, select the concerned scheme.\n**Step 4:** Fill in the required details and upload documents as required. Click on &amp;quot;Submit&amp;quot; to apply.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n&gt; **Contact Us:**\n\nDirector General, Sports Authority of Gujarat\nSport, Youth &amp;amp; Cultural Activities Department\nAdministrative Building, Sector 13-B,\nNear Kh-3 Circle, Near Vavol Railway Crossing,\nBeside EVM warehouse, Gandhinagar - 382016\nContact Number-97140 97760\n<br>\n\n"
